name: Ron DeSantis
tweet: Congratulations to @amazon on its newest distribution center in Florida. This $100 million investment will create 500 jobs for the community and is great news for Volusia County. Florida continues to be the best state in the nation to start or grow a business.

tweet: I look forward to continuing to work with the President and our local, state and federal partners on preserving and restoring Florida’s environment. More here –  https://t.co/cSBSIdaGXP

name: Ron DeSantis
tweet: This federal funding in Everglades restoration will build on our efforts at the state level for critical projects like the EAA Reservoir, the Caloosahatchee Reservoir and the C-44 Reservoir and Stormwater Treatment Area.

name: Ron DeSantis
tweet: Earlier this year, I joined @MarcoRubio and @SenRickScott in requesting $200 million from President @RealDonaldTrump in Everglades restoration funding.   The President answered the call, signing the federal spending bill into law that includes this important investment.
